Mandatory Exercises
● WordCount: Top 10 words excluding “you”, “to”, “your”, “the”, “a”, “of”, “and”
● Popular Movies: create the top 10 aggregated movies with number of ratings more than
200.
● Super Hero: Print the top 10 superhero as a list.

